With just enough THC to help enhance the effects of CBN (naturally occurring cannabinoid known to act as a sleep-aid), enjoy one deliciously rich chocolate taffy just before bedtime. Sweet dreams are made of these!

Available in California, Colorado, Massachusetts, and Oklahoma currently.
